		<title>小奶狗一出生便失去母親！好心女子收留竟發現狗爸默默守候 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/01/%e5%b0%8f%e5%a5%b6%e7%8b%97%e4%b8%80%e5%87%ba%e7%94%9f%e4%be%bf%e5%a4%b1%e5%8e%bb%e6%af%8d%e8%a6%aa%ef%bc%81%e5%a5%bd%e5%bf%83%e5%a5%b3%e5%ad%90%e6%94%b6%e7%95%99%e7%ab%9f%e7%99%bc%e7%8f%be%e7%8b%97/</link>
		
