		<title>貓咪能知道自己名字嗎？飼主忽略的「這些」細節曝光 !</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/01/%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e8%83%bd%e7%9f%a5%e9%81%93%e8%87%aa%e5%b7%b1%e5%90%8d%e5%ad%97%e5%97%8e%ef%bc%9f%e9%a3%bc%e4%b8%bb%e5%bf%bd%e7%95%a5%e7%9a%84%e3%80%8c%e9%80%99%e4%ba%9b%e3%80%8d%e7%b4%b0%e7%af%80/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 時事新聞]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 30 Sep 2025 22:41:21 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
